    <center style="margin-top:15px;">
    </center>
    <center>
    </center>
    <p>
     <strong>
      The Godfather’s SWR Engines Mega Pack Rework v1.0 ATS
     </strong>
    </p>
    <hr/>
    <p>
     The Godfather’s SWR Engines Mega Pack Rework
    </p>
    <p>
     This is a rework of the old SWR Custom Mega engine pack for Australian/NZ Kenworth trucks. This works with my The Godfather’s Kenworth Legend SAR SWR Rework Mod Truck, and this new rework of the old swr customs mega engine pack brings the mega pack back to life and works with ATS 1.59
    </p>
    <p>
     <strong>
      TRUCK LIST
     </strong>
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 404SAR
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 404ST
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 408
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 490
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 500
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 509
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 600
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 608
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 609
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 610
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 650
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 659
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 900
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 908
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 950
     <br/>
     THE GODFATHER’S KENWORTH LEGEND SAR SWR REWORK
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 909
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 604
     <br/>
     KENWORTH 359
    </p>
    <p>
     CREDIT FOR THE REWORK — The Godfather’s Mods Company EST 2021
    </p>
    <p>
     Do note that engines in this pack, when picking one, have the work CASH next to them, so when you see that in the list of engines, you know that is from this mod pack.
    </p>
    <hr/>
    <strong>
     Credits:
    </strong>
    The Godfathers Mods Company EST 2021
    <br/>
    <p style="margin-bottom:3px;">
    </p>
    <hr/>
    <hr>
    <strong>
     How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods
    </strong>
    <br/>
    In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.
    <hr>
     <div>
